reviews.review_text: damn.......... Can an AUD get much better?  I don't think so.  Outstanding work on this.  An amazing show now has an amazing source.  I though the one I had could not get any better.  Well, this does.  Show is a high energy fun-fest with few if any low points.  Deal is a steam roller.  Stranger>Franklins is a lethal weapon.  Fantastic start to finish.  There is no way you can go wrong with this one.
for real Deal for us Deal junkies this is a true treat. tip of the hat to tapers...thanks for rooting this one out, SDH
amazing One of the best audience recording you will ever hear, and one of the smoking-est shows ever!

A trip down memory lane This was my first and only Grateful Dead concert. Downloaded it today (32 years and a few months later) and listening to the drum solo as I write this. How cool is that? Thanks to everyone involved with taping/uploading this show. I am forever Grateful!
